    "The role of 229 responders is represented in Fig 1.",
    "Physicians, research academics and research clinicians were equally represented, with 64 (27.9%), 65 (28.4%) and 67 (29.2%) responders, respectively.",
    "The other responders declared not to be classified as the aforementioned and explained themselves mainly as journalists, students, veterinarians, editors, and pharmacists.",
    "Most of the respondents to this question reported moderate 93 (40.6%) or little 60 (26.2%) familiarity with AI tools.",
    "Only 13 (5.7%) indicated extensive familiarity.Following questions up to Q14 were answered by all participants except for the 10 individuals (4.4%) who indicated no prior knowledge of AI (resulting in their automatic exclusion from answering those specific questions)."
